  <h2 class="sec-title" id="weatherTitle">When to Visit <em>Chandigarh</em></h2>
  <p class="sec-body" id="weatherNote" style="margin-bottom:0">Chandigarh has four distinct seasons. October to March is ideal — cool, clear weather with the Shivalik Hills visible on the horizon. Summers (April–June) are hot but bearable. Monsoon (July–September) turns the city lush green and the Rose Garden spectacularly alive. Winter (December–January) is cool and misty with occasional fog.</p>
