  <h2 class="sec-title" id="sectorsTitle">Chandigarh's <em>Planned Sectors</em></h2>
  <p class="sec-body" id="sectorsNote" style="margin-bottom:18px">Chandigarh has no traditional districts — it is organised into 56 numbered Sectors, each a self-contained neighbourhood of roughly 800m × 1200m. Each sector has its own market, school, health centre and parks. The lower the sector number, the more prestigious the address. Sector 17 is the city centre; Sector 1 is the Capitol Complex.</p>
